import React from "react";
import "./Navbar.css";
import { Navbar, Nav, NavDropdown } from "react-bootstrap";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.css";
// import myLogo from 'public/assets/destinex-logo.png';

function NavBar() {
  return (
		<>
		<Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" bg="dark" variant="dark">
		<Navbar.Brand href="#home">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
		<Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="responsive-navbar-nav" />
		<Navbar.Collapse id="responsive-navbar-nav">
			<Nav className="ml-auto">
				<Nav.Link href="#features">Home</Nav.Link>
				<NavDropdown title="MBBS Abroad" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">MBBS In Russia</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Ukraine</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Armenia</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>
				<NavDropdown title="PG in Abroad" id="collasible-nav-dropdown">
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">PG In Germany</NavDropdown.Item>
					<NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2">MBBS In Europe</NavDropdown.Item>
				</NavDropdown>
				<Nav.Link href="#deets">Contact</Nav.Link>
			</Nav>
		</Navbar.Collapse>
	</Navbar>
		</>
  );
}

export default NavBar;
